<paragraph base="F16125493" id="IFRS11_24" principles="yes"><paranum>24</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 11"/><data name="paranum" value="24"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS11_P0069">A <xref base="F16125600" href="IFRS11_APPA.dita#IFRS11_APPA/IFRS11_TE0006">joint venturer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0212"/></ph></xref> shall recognise its interest in a <xref base="F16125599" href="IFRS11_APPA.dita#IFRS11_APPA/IFRS11_P0084">joint venture<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0211"/></ph></xref> as an investment and shall account for that investment using the <xref base="F16124092" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0018">equity method<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0105"/></ph></xref> in accordance with <xref base="F16217343" href="../ias28/IAS28_TOC.dita#IAS28_TOC0001" id="IFRS11_X0114">IAS 28 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investments in Associates and Joint Ventures</ph></ph></xref> unless the entity is exempted from applying the equity method as specified in that standard.</p></body></paragraph>